title: [Clunk's Weaponry]
description: Beneath a simple stone ceiling, a mounted silver mining pick hangs on one of the speckled granite walls.  Some mithril-braced shelves and a small invar-inlaid table sit in opposite corners while a large granite boulder rests on a speckled granite floor.
Beneath an uneven wooden ceiling, a tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the plain wooden walls.  A plain wooden table sits in one corner while a worn rug rests on the stone floor.
